'''卡迪夫城2010年至2011年球季'''（{{lang-en|'''2010–11 Cardiff City F.C. season'''}}）是[[卡迪夫城足球俱乐部|卡迪夫城足球俱乐部]]在[[英格蘭足球聯賽|英格蘭足球聯賽]]第84個球季，亦是於2003年透過附加賽自[[英格蘭足球聯賽|乙組聯賽〈第三級〉]]升班後連續第8個處於第二級聯賽的球季，上季以第4位結束球季參賽附加賽，在決賽負於[[黑池足球會|黑池]]而無緣升班。

== 記事 ==
* 2010年6月16日高等法院證實球會支付190萬[[英鎊|英鎊]]稅款，並獲撤銷其年內第五次[[清盤|清盤]]申請<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/c/cardiff_city/8742920.stm |title=Court confirms Cardiff City's £1.9m tax payment |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2010-06-16 |accessdate=2010-07-01 |archive-date=2016-03-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160307205214/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/c/cardiff_city/8742920.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。
* 2010年6月30日球會承認未能如期發放職球員六月份薪金<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/c/cardiff_city/8775247.stm |title=Cardiff City admit players' wages have been paid late |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2010-06-30 |accessdate=2010-07-01 |archive-date=2016-03-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160310101649/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/c/cardiff_city/8775247.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。
* 2010年7月6日由於再有130萬[[英鎊|英鎊]]欠稅，球會於8月11日須再到高院應付[[HM稅務海關總署|HM稅務海關總署]]的[[清盤|清盤]]申請；而[[英格蘭足球聯賽|英格蘭足球聯賽]]亦再次禁止球會買賣球員<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/c/cardiff_city/8787586.stm |title=Cardiff hit with transfer embargo due to tax trouble |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2010-07-06 |accessdate=2010-07-06 |archive-date=2020-11-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201105083108/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/c/cardiff_city/8787586.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。
* 2010年8月6日買賣球員禁令獲得取消，新加盟及借用球員可以趕及註冊出戰揭幕戰<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/c/cardiff_city/8890430.stm |title=Cardiff register trio for season as transfer ban lifted |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2010-08-06 |accessdate=2010-08-09 |archive-date=2020-10-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201031170835/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/c/cardiff_city/8890430.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。
* 2010年8月11日在清付稅款後獲高院撤銷[[HM稅務海關總署|HM稅務海關總署]]的[[清盤|清盤]]申請<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/c/cardiff_city/8898206.stm |title=Cardiff City survive winding-up order |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2010-08-11 |accessdate=2010-08-12 |archive-date=2020-10-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201019221159/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/c/cardiff_city/8898206.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。
* 2010年10月25日作客4-0擊敗[[列斯聯足球會|-{zh-hans:利兹联; zh-hk:列斯聯;}-]]，保持26年對賽不敗紀錄，在聯賽四連勝後，積分追平領頭羊[[女王公园巡游者足球俱乐部|-{zh-hans:女王公园巡游者; zh-hk:昆士柏流浪;}-]]，僅以[[得失球差|得失球差]]列次席<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_1/9103978.stm |title=Leeds United 0 - 4 Cardiff |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2010-10-25 |accessdate=2010-10-26 |archive-date=2020-11-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201113070844/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_1/9103978.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。
* 2010年11月17日[[杰伊·博思罗伊德|保夫萊特]]成為球會歷來首位現役球員代表[[英格蘭足球代表隊|英格蘭大國腳]]上陣，以後補身份登場對[[法國國家足球隊|法國]]<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.cardiffcityfc.co.uk/page/NewsDetail/0,,10335~2223744,00.html |title=JAY BOTHROYD MAKES HISTORY |publisher=''cardiffcityfc.co.uk'' |date=2010-11-17 |accessdate=2010-11-18 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20101118214917/http://www.cardiffcityfc.co.uk/page/NewsDetail/0,,10335~2223744,00.html |archivedate=2010-11-18 }}</ref>。

